lenders.name: Cheryl
lenders.occupational_info:
I have a passion for helping the elderly.  I am wanting to start a business to help the elderly and or disabled who need assistance with their activities of daily living.  These particular patients need loving people to care for them and my business will provide the services they need to give them a feeling of independence and will alleviate their family from having to make the hard decision of putting their loved one into a nursing home.

This has been a passion of mine since I was very little.  Having grown up with my Blind Grandmother, I use to help her when needed and have wanted to give back to the elderly or disabled community when I became an adult and feel there needs to be more people in the world willing to do this for this great group of our human population.

lenders.name: Jeffrey
lenders.loan_because:
The micro/student loan is important to me and my future development because it will greatly assist me in changing my career direction.  Going back to school and pursuing new and different employment goals is exciting and necessary at this time in my life.  I know that I possess the required qualities to succeed.  These qualities include determination, a strong work ethic, attention to detail, willingness to learn, drive and motivation.  Unfortunately in today's economic times, obtaining a new degree in Information Technology from ITT Technical Institute, is not feasible without financial assistance.  If I should be fortunate enough to receive a micro/student loan, I will not squander this opportunity, but will consistently work hard and give no less than 110% of myself to my education.
 
In closing, thank you for any and all help.
